Flame-like radiance descends on a creature that the spellcaster (e.g. a [[cleric]] or [[Thrane]] [[wandslinger]]) can see within 60 feet. If the creature is unable to dodge, it is seared by the fiery light (as [[radiant damage|damage type]]).